### 测试1：注册成功（实验5要求截图，核心用例）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "task5_test",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 测试2：登录成功（匹配注册的用户名密码）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "task5_test",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 测试3：密码错误（实验5要求截图，核心用例）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "task5_test",
  "password": "654321"
}

### 测试4：根据ID查询用户（实验5要求，注册成功后id为自增的数字，如1/2）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/1
Accept: application/json

### 测试5：注册用户名已存在（辅助用例，验证唯一约束）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "task5_test",
  "password": "123456"
}